Some PragProg authors are creating the languages and libraries that are generating all the buzz and taking the development community by storm.

And some PragProg authors are traveling the world, sharing their knowledge at conferences, meetups, and private training sessions.

Learn what makes a PragProg author tick, discover how they got where they are, and find out where to see or even meet them next!

